### Tamas Szabo

![arrow-up](https://millenniumintel.com/assets/img/arrow-up.svg)

Based in London and Budapest, Tamas is Millennium’s head of investigative research. He is a
specialist in open-source intelligence gathering and applies his skills in complex
multi-jurisdictional investigations. Before joining Millennium, Tamas led the development of
the investigative practice of our sister firm, Sastre, armed with prior experience at
several leading corporate intelligence firms in London.
